casebody.data:
No. 09-587. Kelly Harrington, Warden, Petitioner v. Joshua Richter. 559 U.S. 935, 130 S. Ct. 1506,

176 L. Ed. 2d 108,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 1449. February 22, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted. In addition to the question presented, parties are directed to brief and argue the following question: “Does AEDPA deference apply to a state court’s summary disposition of a claim, including a claim under Strickland v. Washington, 466 U.S. 668 [104 S. Ct. 2052, 80 L. Ed. 2d 674] (1984)?”

Same case below, 578 F.3d 944.
